Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The food we eat every day is all thanks to this remarkable technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.32,0:02:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet, so many citizens are unaware of it, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. These days, the world is full of people who take the blessings of science for granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see many young people like yourself take an interest in it these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.53,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that you were a pioneer in establishing the food system that Japan enjoys today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite regrettable to see you forgotten in your retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm interested in is the Uka-no-Mitama defense virus's slipshod security system.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a benign virus, but it's designed to attack whatever target is defined in its genetic configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, it's possible to reconfigure the virus to attack the oats themselves instead of pests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Uka-no-Mitama will transform from a god of fertility,\N bringing good harvests, to a demon who brings death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.70,0:03:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the control center that handles the configuration and distribution of the virus
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,was originally converted from a lab in a closed-down university.{real good thinking there, guys}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The facility predates the use of cymatic scans for security.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Its security system uses numeric passwords or, at best, biometric scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you were once in charge there, I should be able to break in easily with your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Professor Kudama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the truth behind the Sibyl System. Behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.01,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kagari die here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We compared and considered the contributions Kagari Shuusei would make to society throughout his life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,against the risk of him revealing the secret of the Sibyl System,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided that the risks outweighed the benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you to decide his worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't even judge Makishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're simply useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The appearance of criminally asymptomatic people,\N whom the Sibyl System cannot analyze, is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how intricate and robust a system you build,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain number of irregularities that deviate from it are bound to appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call that a perfect system?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the system that decides whether people live or die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If we simply add to the functionality and complexity of the system, we can never expect it to be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but to resolve the contradictions by altering the system's management as opposed to its functionality.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,By permitting the appearance of irregularities we cannot manage and taking measures to coexist,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the system achieves perfection in a practical sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can entrust the management of the system to those who deviate from the system.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the most logical conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When we used to have individual personalities and bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we were all asymptomatic persons who deviated from the management of the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there are many among us who acted far more cruelly than Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.89,0:06:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then are you saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that Sibyl is a monster formed from evil people's brains that has been running the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to establish an absolute system, it is necessary to reject relative valuations such as "good" or "evil."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All that is needed is a perfect, infallible system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who manages it and how it is managed are irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In a truly perfect system, its operator's will is not questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Our will itself is the system and the universal standard of value that transcends ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who do you think you are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that each and every one of us previously exhibited numerous problems with our personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, by integrating our minds, we have been able to operate in harmony, attaining a universal standard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The more prejudiced and peculiar the orientations of the individuals who comprise the system,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the more new ideas and values they bring to our perception,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the more flexible and diversified our thinking becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that regard, Makishima Shougo's idiosyncrasy is quite valuable and as such,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we have high hopes that he will become an especially useful member.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We have attained a logical society in which various contradictions and inequalities are resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not the ultimate happiness sought by the rational human mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,By achieving an absolutely perfect system, Sibyl has come to embody that ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point in time, you detest us emotionally and hate us instinctively.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you still cannot deny the Sibyl System's significance and necessity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You accept the fact that the current social order cannot be maintained without Sibyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:08:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You value its necessity above its justifiability,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and we highly value your standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.34,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed Kagari in order to keep your secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunemori Akane possesses a sense of purpose that is shared by the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, we deemed the possibility that you'd reveal our secrets and endanger the system negligibly small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You are... You are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.64,0:08:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask you once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunemori Akane, do you wish for a world without the Sibyl System?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.94,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. You try to nod, but then you hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your own ideals are not clear and well-defined enough to deny the social order achieved at this point.{gotta work on that reality marble, akane}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.79,0:08:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You recognize that the current peaceful society and harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,achieved through law, order, and public well-being are more important than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hence, no matter how much you hate the Sibyl System, or how much you wish to bring it down,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot bring yourself to reject the system on which all those things are built.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.92,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, by analyzing your reactions via cymatic scans, it is easy to grasp your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please cease this futile posturing and let us discuss the matter in earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The goal of this meeting is to establish a collaborative relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Collaborative?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,CID Division 1 is currently in a state of crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to Kougami Shinya's recklessness and Ginoza Nobuchika's breakdown,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the team is starting to show signs of dysfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless a new leader takes the initiative in the investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,we cannot expect success in tracking down Makishima Shougo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Ginoza's... breakdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.22,0:09:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunemori Akane. Because you were caught in an unnecessary inner conflict,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.21,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you have not been able to exhibit your potential capability either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your lack of understanding of the situation has clouded your judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we decided to make an exception and reveal to you the truth behind the Sibyl System.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided that telling you the truth would be the best way to motivate you.{lolwut}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsunemori Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You also disagree with Kougami Shinya taking \NMakishima Shougo's punishment into his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.61,0:10:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You and we both wish to prevent pointless deaths caused by unchecked emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I only want Makishima's crimes to be judged in a fair and just way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those among you who broke the law in the past also need to atone for their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contributions to society are more than enough compensation for the damages we caused in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that convenient?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:11:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Only three minutes left until my future's decided for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do that terribly on the final exam, Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done worse. I wonder what kind of job I'll end up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If we were living in the days before Sibyl existed, it'd be luck of the draw whether we ended up happy or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is a lot better than the old days, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I envy you. You're likely to end up with multiple aptitudes, Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just pick and choose the employer you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still nowhere near as good as Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see what her score was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,700 points. I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, I've always been lucky when it comes to exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,With your exam results and Psycho-Pass, Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got a bright future ahead of you.{barairo pls go}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.97,0:11:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa... My rank is "C"...{better than F}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen, but I'm still shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.53,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine are all office jobs. It'll be tough to work my way up from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you get, Akane?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see, let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Amazing! You've got the necessary aptitude to work in any of the central ministries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. That score really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You could even work at the Public Safety Bureau!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... If I've been recommended all these places, how do I know which one is right for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. What makes you think that someone like me would have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You could become anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You could choose any kind of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've even agonized over it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just like those old folk who lived in the days before Sibyl was created.{note to self, update this in ep2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone used to fumble around, blindly choosing what they were going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that was once our natural way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, the Sibyl System reads your talent
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and tells you the way of living that will bring you the most happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, you're talking about your purpose in life?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even imagined there were people who stressed over things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's tough to deal with. It's always weighing me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But... now I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that being able to worry about those things is what makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the only time people really have value is when they act according to their own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've asked many people about their true, repressed desires and observed their actions all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I think now I can understand how you feel, if only a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you define crime to start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,With the Dominator you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the Sibyl System that governs that gun decide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wrong, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.95,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the mistake in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.15,0:14:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By analyzing a bio-organism's force field read by a cymatic scan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,they figure out how a person's mind works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Science finally discovered the secret behind the human soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and this society changed drastically as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,However, people's wills are not part of that assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just what sort of criteria you use to divide people into good and evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the final judgment of "good" or "evil" that's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is that you come to that decision yourself. That you agonize over it and eventually accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to bear witness to the splendor of man's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to find out once and for all whether it is truly something worth admiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when humans base their lives around Sybil's Oracle, without ever considering what they really want,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do they really hold any value?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying you can decide if someone has value?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That you can judge the worth of their family and friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you determine the value of happiness you've never felt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun and easy. I didn't experience any hardship at all.{this better not be a flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone else always took care of everything for me, and I never even asked myself what was important.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.54,0:15:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Akane, do you think I was still happy that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have become happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You could have searched for the answer anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone can do it, as long as they're alive.{too bad, yuki}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. Tsunemori speaking.{what the hell just happened}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you wander off to in a crisis like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:16:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief ordered me to deliver something to the Ministry of Welfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a murder in Ichikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami's prints have been found at the site. Come here immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be right over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sibyl System, you can hear me, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I want in return for what you asked of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please state your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If I bring Makishima Shougo to you, alive, you will guarantee Kougami Shinya's life in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw his execution order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two things are not logically equivalent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.28,0:16:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your logic.{booyeah}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kougami can't be saved, then I'll let Makishima die as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If push comes to shove, I'll kill him with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do if I don't obey you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to kill me just like you killed Kagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you'll have to go find yourself another pawn you think you can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We will make an exception for Kougami Shinya,\N but only once Makishima Shougo is captured alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.64,0:17:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. What happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Local residents reported seeing someone with that helmet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so we asked around a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we found out that this house, and only this house, had been broken into.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So we rushed in, only to find this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.27,0:17:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim's name is Kudama Nobuaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He used to work for a lab belonging to the Ministry of Agriculture and Forestry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:18:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,but he retired quite a long time ago and lived as an ordinary pensioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The house appears to have been ransacked. We've found Kougami's prints.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would he do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,From the wound on his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima Shougo might have done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this old man had something to do with the next stage of Makishima's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami figured it out and hurried over here, but he was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami really is one step ahead of us, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, what possible reason could Makishima have to kill this geezer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to investigate a crime scene that's already been turned inside out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.47,0:18:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think Kougami's highest priority would be right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Preventing Makishima from getting away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what would his second highest priority be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying out of our reach until he can kill Makishima, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's think about things in that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Kougami, who got here before us, had hidden the body somewhere hard to find?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,While Kudama Nobuaki remained missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we would have continued on a wild goose chase,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,giving Kougami more of a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.09,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It would've been the best way for him to buy some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But he didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kougami isn't the overconfident type.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd account for the possibility that he might fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave clues that others could use to stop Makishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The question is when we'll pick up on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's testing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Testing our determination to pursue Makishima against his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lack that determination, you'll end up stuck here while he goes on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Perform a scan focused on the victim's throat and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.95,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.16,0:20:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A foreign, metallic object has been detected inside the victim's airway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.12,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you should leave this to Forensics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That would only increase Kougami's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.80,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If we want to catch up with him, we have to do this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinse it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an audio recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kougami, former Enforcer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving this message for the Bureau's detectives when they turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.72,0:20:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim is Kudama Nobuaki, a former Doctor of Agricultural Sciences.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.71,0:20:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in charge of the development of the Uka-no-Mitama virus,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,a disease countermeasure for hyper-oats.{HYPER OATSSSSSSSSSS}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.21,0:20:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He was considered to be the biggest contributor to Japan's achievement of complete food autonomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Makishima Shougo met with Professor Kudama to learn how to destroy the granary in Hokuriku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and then killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He gouged out the eyeballs from the victim's skull and cut off all his fingers at their second joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have needed them in order to break through some form of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudama's old laboratory is an antiquated facility with biometric-based security instead of the newer cymatic scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's located at Izumo University, and the lack of security stands out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.75,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This lab is currently used as the control center for the Uka-no-Mitama virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's Makishima's target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans to destroy the whole granary?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he intend to commit bio-terrorism all on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry. We still have time.
